sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant A as Admin (Browser)
    participant NG as Nginx
    participant API as Flask API
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant RD as Redis

    Note over A,RD: 1. Admin Login (same 2-step MFA flow as Patient)

    A->>NG: POST /api/auth/login {email, password}
    NG->>API: Forward request
    API->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email=... AND role=admin
    DB-->>API: user row
    API->>API: bcrypt compare (timing-safe)
    API->>RD: SET mfa_pending_user_id in session
    API-->>A: 200 {message: "MFA required"}

    A->>NG: POST /api/auth/verify-mfa {totp_code}
    NG->>API: Forward request
    API->>RD: GET mfa_pending_user_id from session
    API->>API: pyotp.TOTP(mfa_secret).verify(totp_code)
    API->>RD: Regenerate session, SET user_id + role=admin
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_log (login_success)
    API-->>A: 200 {role: "admin", username}

    Note over A,RD: 2. User Management

    A->>NG: GET /api/admin/users
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: SELECT users (emails masked in response)
    DB-->>API: users list
    API-->>A: 200 [users]

    A->>NG: POST /api/admin/users/{user_id}/suspend
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: UPDATE user SET locked_until='9999-12-31'
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_log (account_suspend, success)
    API-->>A: 200 {message: "User suspended"}

    A->>NG: POST /api/admin/users/{user_id}/activate
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: UPDATE user SET locked_until=NULL, failed_login_attempts=0
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_log (account_activate, success)
    API-->>A: 200 {message: "User activated"}

    A->>NG: POST /api/admin/users/{user_id}/role {role}
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: UPDATE user SET role=new_role
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_log (role_change, success)
    API-->>A: 200 {message: "Role updated"}

    Note over A,RD: 3. Trial Management

    A->>NG: GET /api/admin/trials
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: SELECT all trials (all statuses)
    DB-->>API: trials list
    API-->>A: 200 [trials]

    A->>NG: POST /api/admin/trials {title, description, phase, sponsor, risk_level, spots_total, ...}
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>API: Validate & sanitise all fields, check field length limits
    API->>DB: INSERT trial (status=recruiting)
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_log (trial_create, success)
    API-->>A: 201 {trial_id, message}

    Note over A,RD: 4. Audit Log Review

    A->>NG: GET /api/admin/audit-log?page=1&per_page=50
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: SELECT audit_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 50
    DB-->>API: paginated audit entries (with hash chain)
    API-->>A: 200 {logs, total, pages}

    Note over A,RD: 5. Compliance Report

    A->>NG: GET /api/admin/compliance-report
    NG->>API: require_role(admin) verified
    API->>DB: COUNT users by role, COUNT trials by status
    API->>DB: COUNT participants by consent_status
    API->>DB: COUNT audit_logs by outcome
    DB-->>API: aggregated stats
    API-->>A: 200 {users, trials, participants, audit_summary}
